parameters:
...I see. So, it's already the end, huh. Even from your
perspective...

\SE[47]...Yes. Miss is excellent. \SE[48] Diligent,
talented... above all, hardworking. \SE[47] Normally, she
wouldn't allow others to follow her.

\SE[37]...However, this time the opponent was too bad.
\!\SE[38]It seems that the level of her is unprecedented
even in the school.

I have relied on you... a lot. Especially, our daughter has
opened her heart to you. ...Thank you for everything up
until now.

Can I be alone for a moment...? I want to gather my
thoughts...

I have never cursed my own powerlessness as much as I did on
this day. In the end, I was just a powerless cat.

At the funeral of my husband... The young lady never shed a
tear. In order to not tarnish her respected father... As the
head of the family, she acted strongly and composed herself.
I could only... clench my fists.
